REQUIRED

Before installing this software, please check you have installed following
modules (and its dependencies):

   Gtk2
   Gtk2::Ex::Simple::List
   Gtk2::GladeXML
   YAML
   XML::Simple
   Image::Magick
   LWP::UserAgent
   Locale::gettext
   Net::DBus
   Net::DBus::GLib
   Net::OAuth

If you install from source, you may need msgfmt too (from gettext package).

INSTALLATION

To install this software type the following command as root:

   make install

**
